      "content": "i appreciate you saying that, i really do. but it still feels so hopeless. like, even if the system is the problem, i still have to live *in* the system. i'm just so tired of the fight. sometimes i wonder if there's a point to even trying to fix things when the outcome is always the same. is it even worth it to keep pushing through this much hurt?",
